title: Professional Membership & Insurance For Complementary Therapists | IICT
author: Natalie Robb
description: IICT provides professional recognition and access to comprehensive insurance for complementary therapists who work in a wide range of modalities. Join now.
cleaned_text: I recently joined IICT and found the whole process very easy and streamlined. Communication was excellent. I was very happy with the pricing also. Thank you. Join now and we'll plant a tree for you. 8,456 trees already planted as part of our global reforestation partnership with One Tree Planted.
